1.judged_meaning: general term for any insect or similar creeping or crawling invertebrate
1.precontext: Anna was having a tough week. Her room was a mess, and her computer kept crashing. Frustrated by everything going wrong, she called Jen.

1.example_sentence: The garden was full of bugs.
